====Statistics====
* According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yamashita'' is the 12500<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 2480 individuals. ''Yamashita'' is most common among Asian/Pacific Islander (78.83%) and Mixed Race (11.45%) individuals.
